title: ARTISTA
details: ARTISTA is an art initiative group in the civil department. The group is run by the students and for the students. It is not just bonded to the civil department but open for all the students from all over college. Student make sketches, paintings, write articles and display it on the ARTISTA board. Every month the theme based programme has been arranged where students get together to share their thoughts through art and experience. It is a best practice in the department for extracurricular activities. This culture has been motivating students to work together. Artista is the bonding culture between all the students in department.
